(25, 25, 'OM6.0|P1|13|1', 'OM REV 6.0', 'BCAA', 'AMC1 ORA.ATO.230(b)(a)(6)', 'Operations Manual (OM)', 'PART 1', 13, 1, 'Preparation of flying programme (restriction of numbers of aircraft in poor weather).', 'Who is responsible for the flying training programme/dispatching (A/C or FSTD)?', 'Part 1 – Ch. 4.2', 'Yes', NULL),
