(27, 27, 'OM6.0|P1|13|3', 'OM REV 6.0', 'BCAA', 'AMC1 ORA.ATO.230(b)(a)(6)', 'Operations Manual (OM)', 'PART 1', 13, 3, 'Preparation of flying programme (restriction of numbers of aircraft in poor weather).', 'How is a flight booked (by a student or the ATO)?', 'Part 1 – Ch. 4.2', 'Yes', NULL),
