(29, 29, 'OM6.0|P1|13|5', 'OM REV 6.0', 'BCAA', 'AMC1 ORA.ATO.230(b)(a)(6)', 'Operations Manual (OM)', 'PART 1', 13, 5, 'Preparation of flying programme (restriction of numbers of aircraft in poor weather).', 'What are the restrictions in terms of A/C numbers that the training staff can supervise at the same time in case of poor weather?', 'Part 1 – Ch. 4.2', 'Yes', NULL),
