(58, 58, 'OM6.0|P1|25|1', 'OM REV 6.0', 'BCAA', 'AMC1 ORA.ATO.230(b)(a)(18)', 'Operations Manual (OM)', 'PART 1', 25, 1, 'Pilots’ log books.', 'Explain how the Pilot’s logbook of the students and the FIs must be fulfil for each type of flight (DUAL, PIC, SPIC, NAV, skill test,…). All flights shall be logged in UTC. The reference of the training lesson must be specified in the “remarks” column of the logbook. Each entry in the student logbook shall be checked by the FI.', 'Part 1 – Ch. 5.3', 'Yes', NULL),
